{"tid":469984,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果基督教從未存在過，世界又會變成點？","createTime":"2017-11-16T00:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T16:54:21.000Z","uid":108894,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6262d2ac95ff0452424b89171926dcf4d062de","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"之前我曾經講過少少基督教嘅事，不過大家都知連登某D人最鍾意屌基督教嫁啦，甚至我見過基督教要滅絕世界先可以安定嘅講法，既然如此，不如真係諗下如果基督教從來唔存在世界又會係點<br />\n我自己覺得世界冇左基督教都會一樣咁轉，不過歐洲會同中東一樣會要人嚴守宗教規條 (天主教)<br />\n香港嘅信仰會更接近中國，黃大仙廟佛寺等等週街都係<br />\n羅馬教宗係世界影響力大增，甚至有能力干預聯合國<br />\n(抱歉，對世界形勢唔太熟悉，唔講太多，還請巴打多多補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而我呢？<br />\n我冇基督教其實都冇咩事嘅，最多掂黃掂賭掂酒同份人冇咁善良者，都係一個正常香港人，不過亦因此好難搵到真心朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b2e077847427487da9e2a85349d6943fd7d570","tid":469984,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":10,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"如果如果<br />\n<br />\n點解你條柒頭咁多FF"},{"pid":"dd81dd73e189a0cda5cab4e434274d660d4bf32d","tid":469984,"uid":27609,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:44:57.000Z","msg":"打埋d垃圾"},{"pid":"e0962e092919f9f544dd7c3501441f4f22f438b1","tid":469984,"uid":78574,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"1. 天主教都係基督宗教<br />\n2. 基督新教都大把人黃賭毒"},{"pid":"9d0c7d7df93730ef22917db9c9c5fc702ba6d342","tid":469984,"uid":10818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我曾經講過少少基督教嘅事，不過大家都知連登某D人最鍾意屌基督教嫁啦，甚至我見過基督教要滅絕世界先可以安定嘅講法，既然如此，不如真係諗下如果基督教從來唔存在世界又會係點<br />\n我自己覺得世界冇左基督教都會一樣咁轉，不過歐洲會同中東一樣會要人嚴守宗教規條 (天主教)<br />\n香港嘅信仰會更接近中國，黃大仙廟佛寺等等週街都係<br />\n羅馬教宗係世界影響力大增，甚至有能力干預聯合國<br />\n(抱歉，對世界形勢唔太熟悉，唔講太多，還請巴打多多補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而我呢？<br />\n我冇基督教其實都冇咩事嘅，最多掂黃掂賭掂酒同份人冇咁善良者，都係一個正常香港人，不過亦因此好難搵到真心朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n規條最嚴係基督教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0357cb27d4ccd292791a2f014ffb0d1659f6896","tid":469984,"uid":67864,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"要信仰先保持到自我 證明你垃撚圾"},{"pid":"ad9484be0044ac3ef35481e8cd702d23f159c14d","tid":469984,"uid":21310,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d99c4089e3e46ff46243d5b4aa9ceb4d661cc625","tid":469984,"uid":9887,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"你條廢閪信教信到一知半解仲開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代仲走去敵視天主教"},{"pid":"24115cc6b72531220bedd2e2181228abfb04abc7","tid":469984,"uid":42735,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲冇一千年既dark age<br />\n而家我地應該搞緊太空殖民"},{"pid":"e954144060bdbb6f17d4d83ea1baf597e7d7a8d9","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條廢閪信教信到一知半解仲開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代仲走去敵視天主教</blockquote><br />\n天主教中古時代係大都知，我又點解要敵視天主教，大家都係同一個神，基督教係天主教分出黎者係天主教都係朋友<br />\n同埋我屌你老味我想認真探討下你地又黎挑起罵戰，食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc21028355643eb345061f509d3bc324a27a4f20","tid":469984,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"無基督教的話，耶穌一早變左習近平"},{"pid":"ceaf03750f485427f51555957a93226763719fe8","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要信仰先保持到自我 證明你垃撚圾</blockquote><br />\n人性係十分軟弱<br />\n學好三年，學壞三日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911ca4581e8237a7bb46002d760974b41a713c10","tid":469984,"uid":120499,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街"},{"pid":"65b212a6c1b056ff3ba1e262bad8b6366dcdb70a","tid":469984,"uid":683,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"基督教={新教，天主教，東正教}<br />\n<br />\n新教=香港人口中既「基督教」"},{"pid":"7de4c11002fb61413da3e60b748a7f0c2217793c","tid":469984,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n應該咁講 冇聖經呢樣野 世界會點 應該會和平好多"},{"pid":"c85392925500528bc2c7969c4c78907e01846e6e","tid":469984,"uid":9887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你條廢閪信教信到一知半解仲開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代仲走去敵視天主教</blockquote><br />\n天主教中古時代係大都知，我又點解要敵視天主教，大家都係同一個神，基督教係天主教分出黎者係天主教都係朋友<br />\n同埋我屌你老味我想認真探討下你地又黎挑起罵戰，食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎就話冇新教，教宗權力會影響聯合國，啲人又會保守，就算唔係敵視都係借啲而唱衰天主教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b2f7af857bf67f7ef21ebdf685e2026e1897e3","tid":469984,"uid":105033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"無左班臭雞扮聖女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c8717b828a6ba82f3aaa00a4dd66cce3b9b368","tid":469984,"uid":157710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:09:56.000Z","msg":"世界和平"},{"pid":"f150fdc7ca214b7a18e0f16c12d17006324ece06","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n應該咁講 冇聖經呢樣野 世界會點 應該會和平好多</blockquote><br />\n但係穆斯林同天主教東正教一樣會衝突<br />\n當然如果連呢D教都冇埋世界就真係和平啦，但生活係裡面嘅人幸唔幸福就唔知啦"},{"pid":"f277788ffe9b3440009067f0ef85d9a4a0890010","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你條廢閪信教信到一知半解仲開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代仲走去敵視天主教</blockquote><br />\n天主教中古時代係大都知，我又點解要敵視天主教，大家都係同一個神，基督教係天主教分出黎者係天主教都係朋友<br />\n同埋我屌你老味我想認真探討下你地又黎挑起罵戰，食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎就話冇新教，教宗權力會影響聯合國，啲人又會保守，就算唔係敵視都係借啲而唱衰天主教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀下史啦<br />\n事實新教未興起天主教就係咁<br />\n都冇左新教去推動改變時，又會有幾多變化"},{"pid":"f0422727b98cd4c8634484ad95e55501ba90d8fc","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界和平</blockquote><br />\n中東少左一個世仇對象，或者可以和平少少嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dbc75b50a3a7b775a887de5ba62840aa7f2e90","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n其實一般穆斯林好平和的<br />\nISIS等恐怖份子只係好小好小部分，而且基本上全部正常穆斯林團體都係屌9佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d0ebd81f01404888372368ab7483daad4a2169","tid":469984,"uid":53619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"所有牧師失業"},{"pid":"38650b963ae558772da0e6e6b600880dca04aa6b","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有牧師失業</blockquote><br />\n牧師點會失業<br />\n因為已經唔會存在<br />\n冇基督教世界只會有神父"},{"pid":"49748a884dc3fcf65aa14d41cb29ec4f7abb346c","tid":469984,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你條廢閪信教信到一知半解仲開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代仲走去敵視天主教</blockquote><br />\n天主教中古時代係大都知，我又點解要敵視天主教，大家都係同一個神，基督教係天主教分出黎者係天主教都係朋友<br />\n同埋我屌你老味我想認真探討下你地又黎挑起罵戰，食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎就話冇新教，教宗權力會影響聯合國，啲人又會保守，就算唔係敵視都係借啲而唱衰天主教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀下史啦<br />\n事實新教未興起天主教就係咁<br />\n都冇左新教去推動改變時，又會有幾多變化</blockquote><br />\n無新教天主教一樣會冧<br />\n除住科技發展哲學進步，歷史係有必然性"},{"pid":"73f13f358237e53fb6ba6c2069bbd8689edc72bf","tid":469984,"uid":12618,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"會少好多岸鳩"},{"pid":"c2682a41fabe58f55970de08c83e08a8e71b9232","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會少好多岸鳩</blockquote><br />\n穆斯林夠出左ISIS<br />\n美國"},{"pid":"3941057b130728dbd2aed807154c84a9a684862d","tid":469984,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要信仰先保持到自我 證明你垃撚圾</blockquote><br />\n好多人以為自己控制到自我<br />\n好似你咁<br />\n其實係自我過大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自我控制係一種技能<br />\n大把人戒唔到煙，酒，黃，賭，毒<br />\n很多人