75e07641f8d701","tid":469984,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個命題真係大到唔知點答<br />\n就算你斷代到古代史時間相對短D<br />\n單單係冇基督教對羅馬帝國影響都已經唔係非一般地大</blockquote><br />\n所以大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n討論唔係問題<br />\n但斷代講囉<br />\n如果唔係太大喇"},{"pid":"2edff5b6e2df4b92ab35cb5f251d6a3263e3fe4d","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無基督就無十字軍東征，無東征，成個歐洲就會穆斯林哂，全世界無豬肉食<br />\n而家無基督呢樣野，歐洲君主少咗樣權力制衡，分分鐘好似變成支那咁君權神授</blockquote><br />\n十字軍東征其實唔完全係宗教原因<br />\n有佢既世俗原因係到</blockquote><br />\n十字軍根本係當時歐洲佬打住宗教旗號嘅野蠻侵略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一D打住宗教旗號嘅活動同團體可以好有煽動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b32d5848384ba2edfe857315e29004e5a5f5b1","tid":469984,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"逃學威龍少咁段經典"},{"pid":"b6125c1a60ab30e953f36692d32702ad5696e3f5","tid":469984,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逃學威龍少咁段經典</blockquote><br />\n會改做讀佛教學校<br />\n抄佛經"},{"pid":"c3817fbb911a21a1338233eb5447453fda84395c","tid":469984,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"早期自由主義係用上帝立論，<br />\n上帝賦予每個人天賦人權。<br />\n無神學，唔會出現普世人權。<br />\n我地可能仲做緊傳統農奴。"},{"pid":"b4d2362102fabcb78e28dc7b10a405430257c431","tid":469984,"uid":73611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"不如樓主讀下基督宗教史先開post 啦<br />\n新教出現到同天主教對歐洲社會既影響力下降有絕對關係<br />\n同埋冇新教，都有大把天主教傳教士去中國......."},{"pid":"b8c75990b7dc1b59c7d737b422c46c3ba4bb462c","tid":469984,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早期自由主義係用上帝立論，<br />\n上帝賦予每個人天賦人權。<br />\n無神學，唔會出現普世人權。<br />\n我地可能仲做緊傳統農奴。</blockquote><br />\n佛陀。。。。"},{"pid":"5d581020118ec6996d08a6e61078d1291592f4c0","tid":469984,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如樓主讀下基督宗教史先開post 啦<br />\n新教出現到同天主教對歐洲社會既影響力下降有絕對關係<br />\n同埋冇新教，都有大把天主教傳教士去中國.......</blockquote><br />\n基督教好似係泛稱黎。。"},{"pid":"8768cb29eafe275b4d4249d65e2bddfeefcdce3d","tid":469984,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T22:57:29.000Z","msg":"宗教=思想控制工具=垃圾<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4afa668b373f6e3fdaa063ab001274d8ce318d1","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如樓主讀下基督宗教史先開post 啦<br />\n新教出現到同天主教對歐洲社會既影響力下降有絕對關係<br />\n同埋冇新教，都有大把天主教傳教士去中國.......</blockquote><br />\n基督教好似係泛稱黎。。</blockquote><br />\nYes<br />\n不過既然香港人用基督教同天主教分開新教同天主教，我就用啦"},{"pid":"56aa2f27f9b0a3d4561e899a8d51a8c05d63269d","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宗教=思想控制工具=垃圾<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你思想真係不受控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdabc1782986338b9832a3f1593a636d5225543a","tid":469984,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宗教=思想控制工具=垃圾<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你思想真係不受控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分程度，起馬我相信既係實質既科學，而唔係斥諸無知既宗教"},{"pid":"c6acfae4f1f98592d6dcf25cb34de76680d442e5","tid":469984,"uid":158503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我曾經講過少少基督教嘅事，不過大家都知連登某D人最鍾意屌基督教嫁啦，甚至我見過基督教要滅絕世界先可以安定嘅講法，既然如此，不如真係諗下如果基督教從來唔存在世界又會係點<br />\n我自己覺得世界冇左基督教都會一樣咁轉，不過歐洲會同中東一樣會要人嚴守宗教規條 (天主教)<br />\n香港嘅信仰會更接近中國，黃大仙廟佛寺等等週街都係<br />\n羅馬教宗係世界影響力大增，甚至有能力干預聯合國<br />\n(抱歉，對世界形勢唔太熟悉，唔講太多，還請巴打多多補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而我呢？<br />\n我冇基督教其實都冇咩事嘅，最多掂黃掂賭掂酒同份人冇咁善良者，都係一個正常香港人，不過亦因此好難搵到真心朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得 宗教/科學/皇室 or 隨便一樣野都可以稱做信仰 <br />\n東方社會規則源自於歷史教化，西方社會規則就源自宗教<br />\n如果真係冇宗教，人類社會會冇左某程度上秩序<br />\n而宗教權力又或者一D極端信仰者只係意外副產品<br />\nbtw我無信仰"},{"pid":"56e5b14c4b449c81cd4767be389fc912bfdfbafb","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>宗教=思想控制工具=垃圾<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你思想真係不受控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分程度，起馬我相信既係實質既科學，而唔係斥諸無知既宗教</blockquote><br />\n科學仲係有好多野難以證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f57e436bd0e93b5cf8b1b27d296b977f2cf707","tid":469984,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦"},{"pid":"b5c5fc264c1a93d7b4fb78c400470ad5f75315df","tid":469984,"uid":54046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n穆斯林係猶太教既復興呀ching"},{"pid":"938d19f82bfc82c0c39d1727ecac5bc12177a65e","tid":469984,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"會無左西方文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e29614691641b902e131a68ea216515bc88c970","tid":469984,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"科學起碼進步多幾百年，樓上講嗰d奴隸制,民主都好似唔太關耶教事，奴隸制係發現黑人好恰，之後用黑奴取代，民主主要係美國獨立/法國獨立開始更加唔關事"},{"pid":"e330b27f1003a6963b8eb8daa3af7714fc82f3b2","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n基督教同穆斯林歷史上雖然大有關係但應該係獨立存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e90050dd049a14114468f22715734f8cbd1ce9","tid":469984,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n穆斯林係猶太教既復興呀ching</blockquote><br />\n你都傻嘅<br />\n同係亞伯拉罕諸教丶反對神化先知丶唔食豬肉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔代表</strong></span>佢係猶太教嘅復興。"},{"pid":"4b7d6a9ac07b763561e6170b5d93d8ca981b4b25","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會無左西方文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會冇<br />\n只係個文化唔同左"},{"pid":"88987f722f0395e6ddc65e45a7d68de32a96754e","tid":469984,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n基督教同穆斯林歷史上雖然大有關係但應該係獨立存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇咗基督教，可蘭經就改寫，穆罕默德就取代耶穌，之後連登仔就會開post，問「如果伊斯蘭教冇存在過會點」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac1d1066dda0388d05da5a019be5dffbb0c82d5","tid":469984,"uid":139277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"信基督教就一定善良啲 唔掂黃賭毒 多啲朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130ceae4215093fbc4c0cd13867b5b259639e1e3","tid":469984,"uid":54046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n穆斯林係猶太教既復興呀ching</blockquote><br />\n你都傻嘅<br />\n同係亞伯拉罕諸教丶反對神化先知丶唔食豬肉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔代表</strong></span>佢係猶太教嘅復興。</blockquote><br />\n你可以唔當回教係猶太教既復興<br />\n但回教認為佢地自己係正道既復興"},{"pid":"0cae4b4d56f72b76a643cc1e290d7b2ec052e430","tid":469984,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無耶教，穆斯林會收哂你地非信徒既皮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經慢慢係咁樣發展<br />\n<br />\n耶撚係有問題，但穆撚仲更加仆街</blockquote><br />\n無耶教就冇穆斯林啦</blockquote><br />\n穆斯林係猶太教既復興呀ching</blockquote><br />\n你都傻嘅<br />\n同係亞伯拉罕諸教丶反對神化先知丶唔食豬肉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔代表</strong></span>佢係猶太教嘅復興。</blockquote><br />\n你可以唔當回教係猶太教既復興<br />\n但回教認為佢地自己係正道既復興</blockquote><br />\n搞笑係，回教話阿當被趕出伊甸園後要在地上守嘅規條同而家差唔多<br />\n即係唔准亂倫啦<br />\n但佢地又相信全世界人類都係阿當子孫<br />\n有d教派仲相信挪亞方舟後只有挪亞兒子們先生到後代<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6aa9493540219f5e720a30baa7df0aaef1f0c7","tid":469984,"uid":158677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:54:19.000Z","msg":"心靈軟弱既人先會信教 我唔會話你錯 只會話你廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8ae5f018c4e6e5d2d4b29aacd8d8c9d7c4dcf1","tid":469984,"uid":66340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"應該會變得好美好<br />\n基督教逼害死左好多科學天才<br />\n如果無天主，基督教<br />\n今日人類應該征服左我地呢個太陽系了"},{"pid":"e1073ae5e7e1843ef2bded612235d43b251300ca","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信基督教就一定善良啲 唔掂黃賭毒 多啲朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定 不過以我看見 好多都幾nice<br />\n你話有冇衰人 實有 不過我冇見到 (表面上)"},{"pid":"00d16254ee514209ff55ef8aab51af4dca701e54","tid":469984,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心靈軟弱既人先會信教 我唔會話你錯 只會話你廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知下你有咩底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968d65e98adb54b5f5d85cb44acbd4d05fa280fe","tid":469984,"uid":139277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>信基督教就一定善良啲 唔掂黃賭毒 多啲朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定 不過以我看見 好多都幾nice<br />\n你話有冇衰人 實有 不過我冇見到 (表面上)</blockquote><br />\n <a href=\"http://hongkongchristianmonitoring.blogspot.hk/2014/01/blog-post_18.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkongchristianmonitoring.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F01%2Fblog-post_18.html%3Fm%3D1&d=vAfC9Q9YMLRu6Awf%2Fp1NvAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8f676972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hongkongchristianmonitoring.blogspot.hk/2014/01/blog-post_18.html?m=1</a><br />\n你視野都幾狹窄下"},{"pid":"9d7e68ace3090709db115ee25e85fff477259694","tid":469984,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"奴隸制應該仲盛行緊 但係會進步左"},{"pid":"6756f3db9ac2d5550973fa39b4ab3525c216427c","tid":469984,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}